OL,3,CBroken lift traps Calne residents
OL,4,Cindoors for 13 weeks
OL,6,FResidents at a retirement complex in
OL,7,Fsay they have been trapped indoors for
OL,8,F13 weeks because the building's lift
OL,9,Fis out of service.
OL,11,FPeople living on the upper floors at
OL,12,FThe Wharf in town centre say not being
OL,13,Fable to get out and about has limited
OL,14,Ftheir social lives, disrupted medical
OL,15,Fappointments and left them feeling
OL,16,Fisolated.
