OL,3,CBroken lift traps Calne residents
OL,4,Cindoors for 13 weeks
OL,6,FVera Tolley, who is in her eighties
OL,7,Fand lives on the third floor, said she
OL,8,Fand her fellow residents were
OL,9,Ffrustrated by the amount of time it
OL,10,Fhas taken to fix the problem, and the
OL,11,Fnumber of activities and outings they
OL,12,Fhave missed since January.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News, she said: "We
OL,15,Fsort of feel that it's part of our
OL,16,Flives gone.
OL,18,F"We're all elderly. We're all between
OL,19,F80 and 90-odd. And you can't get that
OL,20,Fback - what we've missed."
