OL,3,CBroken lift traps Calne residents
OL,4,Cindoors for 13 weeks
OL,6,FGreen Square Accord, the management
OL,7,Fcompany that owns and runs The Wharf,
OL,8,Fsays it took the decision to take the
OL,9,Flift out of service due to frequent
OL,10,Fpower cuts in the building.
OL,12,FThe organisation said there was a risk
OL,13,Fthat someone could get trapped in the
OL,14,Flift as a result.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Green Square Accord
OL,17,Fsaid: "We can confirm the lift at The
OL,18,FWharf in Calne has unfortunately been
OL,19,Fout of service for several weeks.
