OL,3,CBroken lift traps Calne residents
OL,4,Cindoors for 13 weeks
OL,6,F"This is because of a fault with the
OL,7,Fpower supply in the local area which
OL,8,Fhas been identified as an issue for
OL,9,Felectrical energy supplier SSEN to
OL,10,Frectify."
OL,12,FThe management company says its staff
OL,13,Fhave been offering extra support to
OL,14,Fresidents and organising social
OL,15,Fgatherings on landings to help them
OL,16,Ffeel less isolated.
