OL,6,FThe local electricity supplier, SSEN,
OL,7,Fsaid that it had put a temporary
OL,8,Fsolution in place, and that
OL,9,Fconsequently there had not been a
OL,10,Fpower cut at The Wharf since 11 April.
OL,12,FIn a statement, SEEN Distribution
OL,13,Fsaid: "We're working right now to
OL,14,Fdiagnose and fix the fault causing the
OL,15,Fissue with the supply in part of this
OL,16,Fproperty.
