OL,3,CBroken lift traps Calne residents
OL,4,Cindoors for 13 weeks
OL,6,F"As this fault is underground, it
OL,7,Ftakes time do this safely. While we do
OL,8,Fthis, we've reconfigured the local
OL,9,Fnetwork to provide a safe, reliable
OL,10,Fsupply to the property."
OL,12,FSince ITV News spoke to residents at
OL,13,FThe Wharf, they have been told in
OL,14,Fwriting by Green Square Accord that
OL,15,Fthe power supply to the lift is now
OL,16,Fbeing retested and that the company
OL,17,Fhopes it will be back in service by
OL,18,FSaturday 11 May.
